700139f-a.title: Bronx: 149th Street (East) - 3rd Avenue
700139f-a.text:
East 149th Street, at the N.E. corner of Third Ave.
About 1911.
Gift of E.M. Jones.

700011f-a.title: Bronx: 3rd Avenue - 149th Street
700011f-a.text:
2858, 2856 and 2844 Third Ave., east side, at East 149th Street,
Nos. 2858 and 2856 are, respectively, adjoining and at the N.E. corner
of the aforementioned thoroughfares, whereas the 2-story building, on
the extreme right, is at the S.E. corner.
About 1911.
Gift of E.M. Jenks.

700138f-a.title: Bronx: 149th Street (East) - 3rd Avenue
700138f-a.text:
East 149th Street, at the N.E. corner of Third Ave., showing
Nrenovation work in progress on the store front of a 3-story frame house.
The view is westward toward the Third Ave. Elevated.
About 1911.
Gift of E.M. Jenks.
